==Three generations of Hyuga==
After the Tenson Korin there were the Three Generations of Hyuga until '''{{ill|Jimmu's Eastern Expedition|ja|神武東征}}''' when the [[Imperial House of Japan]] was founded.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2021-08-04 |title=みやざきの神話と伝承101：概説 |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804121336/https://www.pref.miyazaki.lg.jp/contents/org/chiiki/seikatu/miyazaki101/shinwa_densho/outline.html |access-date=2022-06-12 |website=web.archive.org}}</ref>

